  <summary>1/30/2001--Introduced.
Seniors' Health Care Bill of Rights of 2001 - Amends part C (Medicare+Choice) of title XVIII (Medicare) of the Social Security Act to increase by five percent per year the payment for Medicare+Choice coordinated care plan contracts entered into for three-year periods.</summary>
